277
00:12:16,719 --> 00:12:17,960
he smiles with joy.

278
00:12:18,479 --> 00:12:19,840
When he hears about your heroic feats,

279
00:12:20,359 --> 00:12:22,200
he is proud of you
while worried about you.

280
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,280
