534
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:23,800
My treacherous son.

535
00:25:26,119 --> 00:25:28,040
Taking a step back for a better chance?

536
00:25:29,199 --> 00:25:29,839
Not bad.

537
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:37,520
